WEBVTT

00:06:25.720 --> 00:06:31.920
to police her use
of the so-called public bathrooms.

00:06:32.440 --> 00:06:33.736
She was four years old.

00:06:33.760 --> 00:06:36.856
She had already been taught
the brutal lesson

00:06:36.880 --> 00:06:41.216
that there was
no bathroom door at preschool

00:06:41.240 --> 00:06:45.440
with a sign on it
that welcomed people like her.

00:06:46.400 --> 00:06:49.640
She'd already learned that bathrooms
were going to be a problem,

00:06:50.760 --> 00:06:53.640
and that problem started with her

00:06:54.560 --> 00:06:56.040
and was hers alone.

00:06:58.840 --> 00:07:01.720
So my friend asked me
to talk to her little daughter,